@ApiGateway_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Health Checks - All Services

### Booking Service Health
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/bookings/health

### Flight Service Health
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/flights/health

### Payment Service Health
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/payments/health

### Notification Service Health
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/notifications/health

### AI Service Health
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/ai/health

### Booking Service - Through Gateway

### Create Booking
POST {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "flightId": "flight456",
  "passengerName": "John Doe",
  "passengerEmail": "john@example.com",
  "numberOfSeats": 2
}

### Get Booking by ID
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/bookings/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012

### Flight Service - Through Gateway

### Create Flight
POST {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/flights
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "flightNumber": "BA123",
  "origin": "New York",
  "destination": "London",
  "departureTime": "2025-11-15T10:00:00Z",
  "arrivalTime": "2025-11-15T22:00:00Z",
  "availableSeats": 150,
  "price": 599.99
}

### Search Flights
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/flights/search?origin=New%20York&destination=London&date=2025-11-15

### Payment Service - Through Gateway

### Process Payment
POST {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": "12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012",
  "userId": "user123",
  "amount": 1199.98,
  "currency": "USD",
  "paymentMethod": "CreditCard"
}

### Get Payments by Booking ID
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/payments/booking/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012

### Notification Service - Through Gateway

### Get User Notifications
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/notifications/user/user123

### Get Booking Notifications
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/notifications/booking/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012

### Get Pending Notifications
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/notifications/pending

### AI Service - Through Gateway

### Chat with AI
POST {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "message": "I want to book a flight from New York to London",
  "sessionId": "session-001"
}

### Get Flight Recommendations
POST {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/ai/recommendations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "origin": "New York",
  "destination": "London",
  "departureDate": "2025-11-15",
  "preferredClass": "Business",
  "maxBudget": 2000
}

### Get Chat History
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/ai/chat/history?sessionId=session-001

### Rate Limiting Test

### Test Rate Limit - Send multiple requests quickly
### (Booking service allows 100 requests per minute)
POST {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "test-user",
  "flightId": "test-flight",
  "passengerName": "Test User",
  "passengerEmail": "test@example.com",
  "numberOfSeats": 1
}

### Test AI Rate Limit - Send multiple requests quickly
### (AI service allows 20 requests per minute)
POST {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "test-user",
  "message": "Hello"
}
